Metadata: A Report on the Washington Sea Grant Program for January 1, 1973 - December 31, 1973
program reports (annual, progress, planning reports, etc)

This report summarizes activities of the Washington Sea Grant Program from January 1, 1973 through December 31, 1973 under a grant from the National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration (NOAA), U.S. Department of Commerce. In this report, highlights of the 1973 program are summarized and published by the University of Washington's Division of Marine Resources, administrative unit for Washington Sea Grant.
